680
00:30:14,060 --> 00:30:16,300
[Yongkyu: I like looking at it,
but I'm terrible at it.]

681
00:30:16,300 --> 00:30:18,080
[Yongkyu: I just don't have an eye for it.]

682
00:30:17,780 --> 00:30:18,370
Really?

683
00:30:18,080 --> 00:30:21,290
[Yongkyu: I only stick to monochrome—
black, white, and gray.]

684
00:30:21,290 --> 00:30:24,780
[Chaebe: What if your partner
loves fashion and clothes?]

685
00:30:24,780 --> 00:30:27,890
[Yongkyu: That's great.]

686
00:30:27,890 --> 00:30:31,170
[Yongkyu: As long as it's not too wild?]
[Chaebe: Yeah.]

687
00:30:29,670 --> 00:30:31,200
As long as it's not too wild.

688
00:30:31,830 --> 00:30:35,300
[Chaebe: What about someone
who tries way too hard with their style?]

689
00:30:35,300 --> 00:30:38,280
[Yongkyu: That's a bit tough for me.]

690
00:30:36,910 --> 00:30:38,170
If they try too hard...

691
00:30:38,280 --> 00:30:40,070
[Yongkyu: I prefer someone
who doesn't take forever to get ready.]

692
00:30:40,070 --> 00:30:42,350
[Yongkyu: And someone
who isn't overly sensitive.]

693
00:30:43,070 --> 00:30:46,560
[Chaebe: Are they still getting ready?]

694
00:30:47,100 --> 00:30:50,790
[Heejin: Oh? What are you guys doing?
Reading magazines?]

695
00:30:47,140 --> 00:30:48,940
-Hey there. -What are you doing?

696
00:30:50,790 --> 00:30:52,460
[Yongkyu: Reading.]

697
00:30:52,460 --> 00:30:53,410
[Yongkyu: Oh, it looks great on you.]

698
00:30:53,410 --> 00:30:54,960
[Chaebe: Totally.]
[Heejin: Really?]

699
00:30:54,960 --> 00:30:56,830
[Yongkyu: Black really suits you.]

700
00:30:58,070 --> 00:30:59,790
[Yongkyu: It looks amazing on you, right?]

701
00:30:59,790 --> 00:31:03,500
[Heejin: Black was basically made for me.
Just kidding.]

702
00:31:03,990 --> 00:31:05,720
[Yongkyu: You've got great taste.]

703
00:31:09,530 --> 00:31:12,790
[Yongkyu: So, how's it going?
Anyone texting you?]

704
00:31:13,560 --> 00:31:15,290
[Heejin: Nope.]

705
00:31:15,290 --> 00:31:17,570
[Yongkyu: Seriously?]
[Heejin: Yeah, total silence.]

706
00:31:17,570 --> 00:31:19,820
[Yongkyu: What was the first message you sent?]

707
00:31:20,850 --> 00:31:21,760
[Yongkyu: Can you share?]

708
00:31:21,760 --> 00:31:23,000
[Heejin: Absolutely not.]

709
00:31:23,000 --> 00:31:24,230
[Yongkyu: Sounds like it wasn't a basic "hi."]

710
00:31:24,230 --> 00:31:25,880
[Heejin: Definitely wasn't a "hi."]

711
00:31:26,350 --> 00:31:28,290
[Heejin: Are you only interested in one person?]

712
00:31:28,290 --> 00:31:29,180
[Yongkyu: Me?]

713
00:31:29,730 --> 00:31:30,970
[Yongkyu: Not really.]

714
00:31:31,190 --> 00:31:33,150
[Joking]
[Heejin: What, 5 choices?]

715
00:31:34,350 --> 00:31:35,730
[Hahaha.]

716
00:31:35,990 --> 00:31:37,670
[Yongkyu: Probably 2.]

717
00:31:38,530 --> 00:31:40,140
[Heejin: Different genders?]

718
00:31:40,580 --> 00:31:42,280
[Yongkyu: Yes.]

719
00:31:45,620 --> 00:31:47,990
[Yongkyu: What about you?
Are you all-in on one person, or...]

720
00:31:48,590 --> 00:31:50,910
[Heejin: I have more than one right now.]

721
00:31:50,910 --> 00:31:53,470
[Heejin: I mean, it's only day 2.]

722
00:31:53,470 --> 00:31:55,170
[Yongkyu: Same here.]

723
00:31:55,170 --> 00:31:59,270
[Yongkyu: Still exploring.]
[Heejin: If I claimed I was all-in on one person
but didn't follow through,]

724
00:31:59,940 --> 00:32:03,630
[Heejin: I'd hate myself for that.]
[Yongkyu: So you want to be true to your word?]

725
00:32:03,630 --> 00:32:06,540
[Heejin: Yeah, I want to back up what I say.]

726
00:32:06,910 --> 00:32:08,330
[Nods in agreement]

727
00:32:07,730 --> 00:32:08,340
Good.

728
00:32:08,590 --> 00:32:10,940
[Yongkyu: So you're just testing the waters first?]
[Heejin: Yeah.]

729
00:32:10,940 --> 00:32:12,520
[Yongkyu: That's a smart approach.]

730
00:32:13,020 --> 00:32:16,820
[Where do Heejin's true feelings lie?]

731
00:32:17,100 --> 00:32:18,440
[Chaebe: Is that Jenga?]

732
00:32:18,440 --> 00:32:20,440
[Yongkyu: Want to play?]
[Heejin: Let's do it.]

733
00:32:20,670 --> 00:32:22,630
-Rock, paper, scissors! -Rock, paper, scissors!

734
00:32:21,040 --> 00:32:24,430
[A brief moment shared before heading out]

735
00:32:22,950 --> 00:32:25,750
-Rock, paper, scissors! -Rock, paper, scissors!

736
00:32:25,890 --> 00:32:28,590
[Sujin: What's the penalty for losing?]

737
00:32:28,590 --> 00:32:30,390
[Yongkyu: What do we have to do?]

738
00:32:31,810 --> 00:32:34,950
[Heejin: If Yongkyu loses, he has to send a text.]

739
00:32:35,270 --> 00:32:37,080
[Sujin: If it's Yongkyu, make him send a photo.]

740
00:32:37,540 --> 00:32:39,290
[A moment ago]

741
00:32:39,700 --> 00:32:41,720
[Yongkyu fell asleep and missed his SBM Talk]

742
00:32:43,210 --> 00:32:45,160
-A photo? -Not a selfie though.

743
00:32:43,580 --> 00:32:45,620
[Sujin: Not a selfie.]

744
00:32:45,620 --> 00:32:48,000
[Sujin: Just a landscape shot or something random.]

745
00:32:48,000 --> 00:32:49,470
[Nods]
[Sujin: A landscape or whatever.]

746
00:32:49,820 --> 00:32:52,560
[Yongkyu: Why do you automatically
assume I'm going to lose?]
[Sujin: You never know!]

747
00:32:52,980 --> 00:32:55,420
[A careful touch]

748
00:32:54,730 --> 00:32:55,800
Seriously, seriously.

749
00:32:55,800 --> 00:32:57,990
[Yongkyu: Why are you following me?]

750
00:32:58,330 --> 00:32:59,630
[Blow air.]

751
00:33:00,340 --> 00:33:05,210
[Trying their best to blow the block over]

752
00:33:05,940 --> 00:33:08,940
[Sujin: Blow on it. Make him mess up.]

753
00:33:08,940 --> 00:33:10,410
[Yongkyu: Not happening, no way, no way.]

754
00:33:10,400 --> 00:33:11,930
-Give it up. -Not happening, no way.

755
00:33:10,410 --> 00:33:11,890
[Heejin: Just give it up.]

756
00:33:12,080 --> 00:33:14,320
[Yongkyu refuses to give up]

757
00:33:12,260 --> 00:33:13,050
Keep trying.

758
00:33:13,050 --> 00:33:14,050
It's not falling.

759
00:33:14,600 --> 00:33:16,860
[On the verge of collapse]
[Sujin: It looks like
the Leaning Tower of Pisa right now.]

760
00:33:16,860 --> 00:33:18,230
[Sujin: Look at it, guys.]

761
00:33:18,550 --> 00:33:21,350
[Just as everyone hoped... Yongkyu loses.]

762
00:33:20,430 --> 00:33:21,240
Nice.

763
00:33:21,240 --> 00:33:21,980
Nice.

764
00:33:21,960 --> 00:33:24,310
[Impressive]
[Sujin: Alright, now you have to text.]

765
00:33:24,560 --> 00:33:26,840
[Sujin: Send a photo and a message.]

766
00:33:27,750 --> 00:33:29,960
[Taking a photo]

767
00:33:30,500 --> 00:33:32,430
[Sujin: Are you going to send it]

768
00:33:32,430 --> 00:33:34,110
[Sujin: and say it's a punishment?]

769
00:33:34,110 --> 00:33:36,800
[Yongkyu: What are the stakes for this round?]

770
00:33:38,070 --> 00:33:39,590
[Sujin: Wait, did you send your SBM Talk yet?]

771
00:33:39,590 --> 00:33:42,730
[Yongkyu: Yeah, about to.]
[Heejin: Ugh, hurry up and send it!]

772
00:33:42,730 --> 00:33:45,100
[Hesitating]
[Sujin: Send it right now.]

773
00:33:47,590 --> 00:33:50,010
[Sujin: Just keep it casual. Don't overthink it.]

774
00:33:50,010 --> 00:33:52,950
[Sujin: Come on, you've got 5 people
to choose from anyway.]

775
00:33:52,890 --> 00:33:53,620
Yeah.

776
00:33:53,010 --> 00:33:55,120
[Hesitating]

777
00:33:55,390 --> 00:33:58,150
[Sujin: You have five options,
though you can text anyone.]

778
00:33:58,150 --> 00:34:00,770
[Yongkyu gets stuck in his head]

779
00:34:03,770 --> 00:34:04,650
[Sujin: Did you send it?]

780
00:34:04,650 --> 00:34:06,580
[Nods]
[Sujin: Did you send it?]

781
00:34:06,890 --> 00:34:09,110
[Carefully]
[Starting the next turn]

782
00:34:09,480 --> 00:34:11,630
[Heejin: Why are my hands shaking so much?]

783
00:34:11,989 --> 00:34:14,679
[Sujin: Wait, sorry, are we still doing a penalty
for this round?]

784
00:34:14,679 --> 00:34:16,739
[Yongkyu: Of course.]
[Sujin: What kind?]

785
00:34:18,750 --> 00:34:20,070
[Heejin: Hold on, hold on, let's decide it first...]

786
00:34:20,070 --> 00:34:22,920
[Sujin: Let's figure it out first.]
[Heejin: Yeah, let's figure it out first.]

787
00:34:23,670 --> 00:34:24,800
Why is this so exhausting?

788
00:34:23,760 --> 00:34:25,580
[Exhausted]

789
00:34:26,810 --> 00:34:29,190
[Sujin: Text someone else again?]

790
00:34:28,659 --> 00:34:29,250
That's brutal.

791
00:34:29,190 --> 00:34:31,560
[Sujin: We won't know who gets it anyway.]
[Heejin: Exactly.]

792
00:34:31,800 --> 00:34:32,340
[Serious]

793
00:34:32,340 --> 00:34:34,179
[Serious]
[Yongkyu: Oh, man, seriously...]

794
00:34:34,179 --> 00:34:37,639
[Yongkyu: Why is everyone moving with me?]
[Sujin: You're the main character today.]
[So much fun]

795
00:34:37,639 --> 00:34:40,219
[Heejin: What kind of photo
are you planning to send?]

796
00:34:40,170 --> 00:34:40,690
Hold on.

797
00:34:40,480 --> 00:34:42,800
[Yongkyu refuses to give up]

798
00:34:40,690 --> 00:34:41,940
So quick.

799
00:34:43,030 --> 00:34:45,050
[Heejin: Look at that determination.]

800
00:34:45,429 --> 00:34:46,500
[Successfully escapes the crisis]

801
00:34:45,969 --> 00:34:46,780
This...

802
00:34:46,500 --> 00:34:48,630
[Chaebe: No way... what am I supposed to do?]

803
00:34:48,770 --> 00:34:49,889
Slowly losing its balance.

804
00:34:48,880 --> 00:34:50,790
[Anxious]

805
00:34:49,889 --> 00:34:50,940
It's totally the Leaning Tower of Pisa right now.

806
00:34:50,790 --> 00:34:52,790
[Yongkyu: Just tap it. Nice and quick.]

807
00:34:53,480 --> 00:34:57,430
[Satisfied]
[Sujin: Wow, how did you do that?]

808
00:34:57,630 --> 00:35:00,690
[And now it's Sujin's turn]

809
00:34:59,110 --> 00:35:00,000
My heart hurts.

810
00:35:00,910 --> 00:35:02,200
[Shaking]

811
00:35:02,630 --> 00:35:03,840
[Heejin: That hurts.]

812
00:35:03,840 --> 00:35:07,160
[Yongkyu: Congrats, congrats. Oh dear.]

813
00:35:07,560 --> 00:35:08,870
[Sujin: No way. Please.]

814
00:35:08,870 --> 00:35:12,040
[Yongkyu: How did you end up picking that color?]
[Sujin: Ah, really? How could this happen?]

815
00:35:12,830 --> 00:35:14,870
[Accepting her fate]

816
00:35:12,890 --> 00:35:13,440
OK.

817
00:35:13,440 --> 00:35:14,500
This round is mine.

818
00:35:15,330 --> 00:35:16,790
Just pull it. Just pull it.

819
00:35:17,220 --> 00:35:20,640
[Sujin loses in the second round]

820
00:35:20,950 --> 00:35:23,860
[Charging up]
[Sujin goes to send a message as her penalty]

821
00:35:30,960 --> 00:35:35,170
[SBM Talk from Yongkyu]

822
00:35:36,700 --> 00:35:38,000
[Surprised]

823
00:35:38,970 --> 00:35:41,600
[Yongkyu sent a photo to Sujin not long ago]

824
00:35:42,460 --> 00:35:46,800
[Yongkyu: I sent Sujin the photos I took.]

825
00:35:46,800 --> 00:35:51,310
[Yongkyu: After my date with Sujin, I got more
and more curious about her.]

826
00:35:51,310 --> 00:35:53,060
[Yongkyu: I have some feelings for her too.]

827
00:35:53,060 --> 00:35:54,810
[Yongkyu: Since Sujin also got a penalty,]

828
00:35:54,810 --> 00:35:57,400
[Yongkyu: she has to send an SBM Talk, so
she should see the message I sent.]

829
00:35:57,400 --> 00:35:58,470
[Yongkyu: She should see it now.]

830
00:35:59,750 --> 00:36:03,300
[Sujin: I was a little flustered when
I saw it... surprised.]

831
00:36:03,300 --> 00:36:08,840
[Sujin: Huh? So he felt that way? I had no idea.]

832
00:36:08,840 --> 00:36:11,790
[Sujin: It made me a little conscious of him.]

833
00:36:12,130 --> 00:36:15,380
[Yongkyu, using the game as an excuse
to express his feelings]

834
00:36:15,830 --> 00:36:19,270
[Sujin learns about Yongkyu's feelings that
she never knew about]

835
00:36:19,920 --> 00:36:22,860
[Will a spark of love ignite between the two?]

836
00:36:23,300 --> 00:36:25,060
[Yongkyu: About 10 minutes left. Last round?]

837
00:36:25,060 --> 00:36:25,920
[Chaebe: Okay, last round.]

838
00:36:25,920 --> 00:36:26,790
[Heejin: Last round. For real this time.]

839
00:36:27,520 --> 00:36:29,940
[Sujin: How about we do this one?]

840
00:36:29,940 --> 00:36:33,500
[Sujin: Let's each say our ideal type—
for guys and for girls.]

841
00:36:33,810 --> 00:36:36,450
[Yongkyu: Or how about the last place
among the same gender?]

842
00:36:36,450 --> 00:36:38,430
[Heejin: Last place among the same gender?]
[Yongkyu: Yeah. Last place among the same gender.]

843
00:36:38,870 --> 00:36:40,320
[Heejin: Ah, hold on.]

844
00:36:41,350 --> 00:36:42,250
This isn't easy.

845
00:36:42,250 --> 00:36:43,950
[Yongkyu: Oh dear.]
[Sujin: Not easy at all.]

846
00:36:43,950 --> 00:36:45,840
[Heejin: Ah, wait, wait, wait.]

847
00:36:46,830 --> 00:36:48,750
[Heejin: It follows me?]

848
00:36:48,160 --> 00:36:48,980
It follows me.

849
00:36:49,440 --> 00:36:52,340
[Yongkyu: Have you decided?]

850
00:36:50,260 --> 00:36:51,260
What do I do? Can I say it?

851
00:36:51,260 --> 00:36:52,260
Have you decided?

852
00:36:52,560 --> 00:36:54,390
[Shaking]

853
00:36:55,270 --> 00:36:56,070
I give up.

854
00:36:55,300 --> 00:36:58,290
[Heejin, giving up without hesitation]

855
00:36:56,520 --> 00:36:57,700
Why don't you try?

856
00:36:57,700 --> 00:36:58,870
Challenge accepted.

857
00:36:58,870 --> 00:37:00,140
[Pouty]

858
00:37:00,140 --> 00:37:01,410
[Heejin: Seriously, do you want
to try it yourself?]

859
00:37:00,600 --> 00:37:01,290
OK, OK.

860
00:37:01,480 --> 00:37:03,950
[Heejin: Try it. Can you really pull it out?]

861
00:37:03,950 --> 00:37:05,840
[Heejin: I really can't do it.]

862
00:37:08,070 --> 00:37:10,110
[Sujin: Wow, you're really good at this.]

863
00:37:10,110 --> 00:37:12,770
[Sujin: Now it's Heejin's turn to answer.]

864
00:37:13,580 --> 00:37:15,770
[On guard]
[Heejin: 7th place among the same gender?]

865
00:37:16,710 --> 00:37:20,400
[Yongkyu: The person furthest from my ideal type
among the same gender?]

866
00:37:22,290 --> 00:37:24,180
[Heejin: I pick...]

867
00:37:26,860 --> 00:37:28,190
[Heejin: Eunchae.]

868
00:37:28,500 --> 00:37:31,030
[Sujin: Really?]
[Heejin: Yes.]

869
00:37:31,030 --> 00:37:32,750
[Sujin: My intuition was wrong again.]

870
00:37:32,750 --> 00:37:35,880
[Yongkyu: Looks like everyone's intuition is off.]

871
00:37:35,880 --> 00:37:38,410
[Sujin: Why? She's cute, though?]

872
00:37:39,510 --> 00:37:42,780
[Sujin: She picked Eunchae as 4th place
among the same gender.]

873
00:37:42,780 --> 00:37:45,370
[Sujin: So aside from Heejin and Eunchae...]

874
00:37:45,370 --> 00:37:49,280
[Sujin: The 1st and 2nd place must be either
Hyeyeon or me.]

875
00:37:49,680 --> 00:37:53,530
[Sujin: So I thought, "Oh, I'm not last place."]

876
00:37:53,530 --> 00:37:57,400
[Sujin: I was really happy at that moment.]

877
00:37:57,670 --> 00:37:59,370
Won't we still be like this tomorrow?

878
00:37:57,760 --> 00:38:02,680
[After the game ends, feelings become clearer]

879
00:37:59,910 --> 00:38:01,480
There's no one left to tell.

880
00:38:03,550 --> 00:38:06,460
[Hyeyeon: Have you ever fallen in love
at first sight?]

881
00:38:06,460 --> 00:38:07,450
[Seungho: I...]

882
00:38:07,750 --> 00:38:09,070
[Seungho: I don't think I'm like that.]

883
00:38:09,070 --> 00:38:11,820
[Seungho: First impressions are really important.
They last a long time.]

884
00:38:11,820 --> 00:38:13,480
[Hyeyeon: So you develop feelings based
on first impression?]

885
00:38:13,480 --> 00:38:14,460
[Seungho: Yeah, that's right.]

886
00:38:14,350 --> 00:38:15,100
First impression.

887
00:38:14,460 --> 00:38:16,760
[Hyeyeon: But you still need to get
to know them slowly afterward.]

888
00:38:16,760 --> 00:38:18,980
[Seungho: It's important, and I value it.]

889
00:38:18,980 --> 00:38:22,230
[Seungho: But it doesn't determine everything.]

890
00:38:22,230 --> 00:38:26,010
[Hyeyeon: Then the time that follows must be
really important, right?]

891
00:38:24,750 --> 00:38:26,110
-Today's date. -Yeah.

892
00:38:26,010 --> 00:38:27,900
[Seungho: Yeah.]

893
00:38:27,900 --> 00:38:28,920
[Seungho: What about you, Hyeyeon?]

894
00:38:30,340 --> 00:38:35,200
[Hyeyeon: I'm the type who easily gets drawn in
by first impressions.]

895
00:38:35,200 --> 00:38:37,690
[Hyeyeon: So when I'm talking to someone,]

896
00:38:37,690 --> 00:38:39,370
[Hyeyeon: if they're a good person,]

897
00:38:39,370 --> 00:38:43,880
[Hyeyeon: I can fall for them pretty quickly.
As long as they're a good person.]

898
00:38:48,560 --> 00:38:51,330
[Hyeyeon, suddenly startled]

899
00:38:50,370 --> 00:38:51,300
What's going on?

900
00:38:57,820 --> 00:38:59,720
[Peeking in]

901
00:39:02,300 --> 00:39:04,660
[Yongkyu: We're here to crash.]

902
00:39:03,060 --> 00:39:04,520
-Hello. -What's going on?

903
00:39:04,910 --> 00:39:05,870
We're hungry too.

904
00:39:05,830 --> 00:39:07,260
[Chaebe: I'm so jealous of your photos.]

905
00:39:05,870 --> 00:39:07,260
-So jealous of your photos. -Jealous.

906
00:39:07,260 --> 00:39:09,060
[Sujin: You two looked like you were
having too much fun.]

907
00:39:09,110 --> 00:39:10,830
-What's going on? -What's going on?

908
00:39:10,300 --> 00:39:11,690
[Seungho: What's going on...?]

909
00:39:13,420 --> 00:39:15,090
[Seungho: I was really surprised.]

910
00:39:15,090 --> 00:39:18,240
[Seungho: What is happening here?]

911
